<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <%- include('shared/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Fredoka One", "Comic Sans MS", sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0078d7, #004a8c);
            color: var(--text-color);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-top: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .howtoplay-content {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            margin-top: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .howtoplay-content::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff4500, #ffcc00, #4caf50, #2196f3);
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        h1::after {
            content: "";
            display: block;
            width: 100px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin: 15px auto 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        h3 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        strong {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .card-examples {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .card {
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(5deg);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .back-to-home {
            display: block;
            margin: 40px auto 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 200px;
        }
        
        .back-to-home:hover {
            background-color: #ff5722;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        .special-card {
            border: none;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .special-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 6px;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        .special-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .special-card h4 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
        
        .rules-section, .strategy-section {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }
        
        .strategy-section {
            background-color: #fff8f0;
        }
        
        .section-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-right: 15px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        
        .tip-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .tip-box h4 {
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px;
                padding-top: 80px;
            }
            
            .howtoplay-content {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            
            h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }
            
            .card-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('shared/header') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="howtoplay-content">
            <h1>How to Play UNO</h1>
            
            <p>Welcome to UNO Online! This guide will teach you everything you need to know about playing UNO, from basic rules to advanced strategies.</p>
            
            <h2>Game Objective</h2>
            <p>The goal of UNO is simple: be the first player to get rid of all your cards. The game is played with a special deck of cards with different colors, numbers, and special actions.</p>
            
            <h2>Card Types</h2>
            
            <h3>Number Cards (0-9)</h3>
            <p>These are the basic cards in four different colors: Red, Blue, Green, and Yellow. Each card has a number from 0 to 9.</p>
            
            <div class="card-examples">
                <div class="card card-red"><span class="card-value">5</span></div>
                <div class="card card-blue"><span class="card-value">2</span></div>
                <div class="card card-green"><span class="card-value">7</span></div>
                <div class="card card-yellow"><span class="card-value">9</span></div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Special Action Cards</h3>
            
            <div class="card-grid">
                <div class="special-card">
                    <h4>Skip Card</h4>
                    <p>When you play this card, the next player's turn is skipped.</p>
                    <div class="card-examples">
                        <div class="card card-red"><span class="card-value">⊘</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="special-card">
                    <h4>Reverse Card</h4>
                    <p>This card changes the direction of play. If play was going clockwise, it now goes counter-clockwise, and vice versa.</p>
                    <div class="card-examples">
                        <div class="card card-blue"><span class="card-value">⟲</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="special-card">
                    <h4>Draw Two Card</h4>
                    <p>When you play this card, the next player must draw two cards and skip their turn.</p>
                    <div class="card-examples">
                        <div class="card card-green"><span class="card-value">+2</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="special-card">
                    <h4>Wild Card</h4>
                    <p>This card can be played on any color. When you play it, you choose what color continues the game.</p>
                    <div class="card-examples">
                        <div class="card card-black"><span class="card-wild-label">WILD</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="special-card">
                    <h4>Wild Draw Four Card</h4>
                    <p>This is the most powerful card. You can play it on any color, choose a new color, and force the next player to draw four cards and lose their turn.</p>
                    <div class="card-examples">
                        <div class="card card-black"><span class="card-wild-label">WILD</span><span class="card-plus4">+4</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rules-section">
                <h2><span class="section-icon">📋</span> Basic Rules</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Starting the Game:</strong> Each player is dealt 7 cards. The remaining cards form the draw pile. The top card is flipped over to start the discard pile.</li>
                    <li><strong>Taking Turns:</strong> On your turn, you must play a card that matches either the color or number of the top card on the discard pile. If you can't play a card, you must draw a card from the draw pile.</li>
                    <li><strong>Playing Special Cards:</strong> Action cards can be played on matching colors or on the same action card. Wild cards can be played anytime.</li>
                    <li><strong>Calling "UNO":</strong> When you have only one card left, you must call "UNO". If you don't and another player catches you, you must draw two cards.</li>
                    <li><strong>Winning:</strong> The first player to get rid of all their cards wins the round!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <h2>Playing UNO Online</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Create an Account:</strong> Sign up to access all game features.</li>
                <li><strong>Join or Create a Game:</strong> From the lobby, you can join an existing game or create your own.</li>
                <li><strong>Game Interface:</strong> Your cards will be displayed at the bottom of the screen. The discard pile is in the center.</li>
                <li><strong>Playing Cards:</strong> Click on a card to play it. If it's a valid move, the card will be played.</li>
                <li><strong>Drawing Cards:</strong> If you can't play, click the draw pile to draw a card.</li>
                <li><strong>Special Actions:</strong> For Wild cards, you'll be prompted to choose a color after playing.</li>
                <li><strong>Calling UNO:</strong> The system automatically calls "UNO" for you when you have one card left.</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="tip-box">
                <h4>Pro Tip!</h4>
                <p>Pay close attention to what cards other players are playing. This can give you clues about what colors they might be collecting or lacking.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="strategy-section">
                <h2><span class="section-icon">🏆</span> Strategy Tips</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Save Special Cards:</strong> Try to save your action cards for strategic moments, especially when someone is down to their last few cards.</li>
                    <li><strong>Watch Other Players:</strong> Pay attention to what colors other players might be collecting or avoiding.</li>
                    <li><strong>Plan Ahead:</strong> Try to keep cards of multiple colors so you have options on your turn.</li>
                    <li><strong>Use Wild Cards Wisely:</strong> Save Wild cards for when you really need them, such as when you have no matching colors.</li>
                    <li><strong>Force Card Draws:</strong> Use Draw Two and Wild Draw Four cards to slow down players who are close to winning.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <a href="/" class="btn back-to-home">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Add any interactive elements if needed
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            console.log('How to Play page loaded');
            
            // Add a subtle animation to cards on page load
            const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card');
            cards.forEach((card, index) => {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    card.style.opacity = '1';
                    card.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                }, 100 * index);
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html> 